  "body": "As a node operator I want the logs to be useful and intelligible.\r\n\r\nOn starting Teku 22.9.1 I see the following\r\n\r\n```\r\n2022-09-20 09:42:22.669 INFO  - MERGE is completed. Stopping.\r\n2022-09-20 09:42:22.669 INFO  - Monitor has stopped\r\n```\r\n\r\nIt's good to see that the merge is completed, but the `Stopping` is a bit alarming - what's stopping? Is it related to the `Monitor` in the next line? If so, what's the `Monitor` and why do I care about it?",
